    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Dear Sir;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "A research group that I am in is presently engaged in the study",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "of the subject of UFOs (Unidentified Flying Objects), sometimes ludicrous-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "-ly termed \"flying saucers\".",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Since our research takes us into every aspect of the subject,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "certain rumors and statements appear which we feel justify an examination",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "to the fullest. One such statement is that, certain federal agencies,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "namely the FBI and CIA, have carried on private investigations of UFOs",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "and/or that such agencies have, at times, worked in conjunction with the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Air Force on its own study of the subject. Another such statement is that,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "agents of the intelligence bureaus (FBI and CIA) have, at times, pres-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "-sured private citizens to keep quiet about the \"mysterious objects\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "that they saw.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
